data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-bath home in desirable neighborhood! This property features a spacious open floor plan with tile floors, a cozy fireplace, and a modern kitchen with granite countertops. Enjoy a large master suite with a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. The backyard oasis boasts a covered patio and lush landscaping. With a 2-car garage and proximity to schools and parks, this home is perfect for families. Don't miss out on this opportunity!,breakfast area, cozy fireplace for those cold winters and immaculate game room to entertain those sports games. Backyardfeatures pergola, custom built shed and a large pad of concrete to host those family gatherings. Conveniently located nearshopping centers and variety of restaurants. Easy access to JFK airport, Beltway 8, FM 1960 and Hwy 69. Schedule yourshowing today before it's gone!
